    "description": "<p>Uniseal Creative Solutions Pte Ltd is the leading technology and solutions provider in sustainable construction sector. We are a Singapore company, proudly owned and founded by Singaporeans with firm belief in circular business model and sustainability as the core of our business. Our wide range of 100% recycled products from green roof, green walls, stormwater management tank systems, green engineering and ecological management systems to level raising pedestal system and even waterproofing as our core specialsation are the results of R&amp;D and innovations. We use plastic waste (polypropylene) and turn them into high performance and high quality 100% recycled product. We have patents, trademarks and design registrations for most of our products and awarded many accrediation and sustainability certifications and endorsement. Our company is a participant of United Nations Global Compact, supporting the 10 principles and Sustainable Development Goals of the United Nations.</p>",
